data.description: Welcome! This 4br/2.5bth w/ 2 car garage beauty nestled on a serene cul-de-sac in a top-rated school district is a true gem. This immaculate residence offers an ideal blend of classic charm & modern convenience, making it the perfect place for you to call home. You will love the spacious primary suite that comes equipped with a walk in closet.  This beauty comes w/ all the kitchen appliances and a washer & dryer.  Plus the owner is leaving the push lawn mower so we will be ready for grass cutting.  Thinking about starting a home gym?  No problem the owner is leaving the exercise equipment in the 4th br.   The 1st bedroom is oversized & would be perfect for a bonus hang out room if you desire.  Let's not leave out the oasis in the backyard.  There is a large deck & the patio furniture and grill come w/ the home.  Off of the deck there is a screened in gazebo that is wired for electricity-perfect for lighting & charging up devices  Plus a fire pit is waiting for you!
